'''Jandarra''' was a small, tubular, purple and green vegetable native to [[Jubilar/Legends|Jubilar]]. Considered a delicacy, the [[Plant/Legends|plant]] would usually only grow after rare rainstorms in the desert which made it hard to cultivate. It was also one of [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo's]] favorite treats.

[[Shalam]] imported it but at a 100% tariff, bringing its worth there down by half the cost, thereby forcing the people of Jubilar to [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggle]] jandarra to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] for processing.

